<!DOCTYPE html> <!-- This file has been dedicated to the public domain under CC0.  See details at bottom. -->
<html xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml' lang='en-CA' xml:lang='en-CA'>
    <head>
        <meta charset='UTF-8'/>
        <title>The wayrepo</title>
        </head>
    <body>
        <p> <!-- ___ HERE DOWN CUSTOM ___ -->
            This file isn’t web-readable yet because I’m still working with the way files in mere source form.
            Please view the source if you want to see what the content properly looks like.
            Here’s <a href='http://reluk.ca/project/way/script/emacs/wayscript_in_editor.png'>
            what wayscript looks like</a> to me, for example.
            </p> <!-- ^^^ HERE UP CUSTOM ^^^ -->
        <way:script xmlns:way='data:,wayscript' xmlns:html='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml'
                        xmlns='data:,wayscript.bit'>
            <!-- <<< deindent -->



<constraint_G way:lid='ever_G' way:link='/theorist/ethics/normative_ethic/#G'>
    Always the wayrepo relates the personal to the endmost goal of the person
    <requirement way:lid='endmost_goal_recording'>
        The wayrepo records one’s endmost goal
        </requirement>
    <requirement way:lid='goalward_recording'>
        The wayrepo records personal expressions that relate to one’s endmost goal
        </requirement>
    <requirement>
        The wayrepo traces and tracks one’s way
        <way:including>
            <r>The wayrepo traces and tracks all the world’s recorded expressions
               that relate to one’s endmost goal</r>
            </way:including>
        <r>
            The record of a way can extend across multiple wayrepos
            <r way:link='#available'/>
            </r>
        <r>
            The <html:a href='http://reluk.ca/project/way/gloss/extend'>extension</html:a>,
               <html:a href='http://reluk.ca/project/way/gloss/collate'>tracing</html:a> and
              <html:a href='http://reluk.ca/project/way/gloss/track'>tracking</html:a>
            of a way happen in the background of awareness
                <!-- from http://reluk.ca/project/way/gloss/backgrounding -->
            <fact>A way can be too big for one alone to monitor and maintain</fact>
            <r way:link='../#backgrounding'/>
            </r>
        </requirement>
    </constraint_G>



<constraint_F way:lid='ever_F' way:link='/theorist/ethics/normative_ethic/#F'>
    Always the wayrepo promotes a maximum, universal sum of personal freedom
    <requirement>
        The wayrepo is personal property, to shape and fill according to one’s will
        </requirement>
    <requirement way:lid='available'>
        A wayrepo of one’s own is available to anyone who wants it
        <r way:lid='public'>
            The wayrepo is a public facility
            <r way:link='../#public_reading'/>
            </r>
        <r way:lid='propagating'>The wayrepo propagates by free copying</r>
        </requirement>
    <belief>
        Personal freedom increases when useful tools are in the hands of the person
        </belief>
    </constraint_F>



            <!-- >>> reindent -->
            </way:script>
        </body>
    </html>

